{"id":155001,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国之声-希腊将出售大量国有资产/","date":"2011-05-24T17:30:26Z","modified":"2011-05-24T17:30:26Z","title":"德国之声 | 希腊将出售大量国有资产","content":"<div>\n<p>雅典<br />为摆脱巨额国家债务，希腊准备出售大量国有财产。希腊财政部在内阁举行危机处理会议后宣布，准备“立即”出售的国有财产包括在电信集团OTE中的股权，在邮政银行以及在塞萨罗尼基(Thesssaloniki)港和皮尔洛斯(Piräus)港的股权。据悉，希腊发放工资和养老金的能力只能维持到7月中旬。因此该国急需欧盟和国际货币基金组织发放下一笔贷款。欧盟和国际货币基金组织为希腊提供的贷款数额总计为120亿欧元。但欧盟和国际货币基金组织迄今并没有为下一步发放贷款开放绿灯。<br /> </p>\n</div>\n<p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15100626%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E5%B0%86%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%89%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}